Interface RenderPipeline

  • All Superinterfaces:
    com.badlogic.gdx.utils.Disposable, Resizeable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CombinedRenderPipeline

    public interface RenderPipeline
extends com.badlogic.gdx.utils.Disposable, Resizeable
    Handles the complete pipeline of rendering internally. The pipeline consists of render pipes.
    Version:
    1.0.0
    Author:
